item.title: Autoclicker 2 clicks
item.dc:creator: @Pwnd Pwnd
item.description:
@Pwnd wrote:

What the fuck?

Ok, you want it to click twice somewhere? Or double click?

[code]
program WTFNIG;

const
Xa = 00;
Ya = 00;

begin
ClickMouse(Xa, Ya, True);
Wait(10);
ClickMouse(Xa, Ya, True);
end.[/code]

If you want it to keep clicking:

[code]
program WTFNIGWithRepeat;

const
Xa = 00;
Ya = 00;
Time = 100; // Time in between clicks

begin
repeat
ClickMouse(Xa, Ya, True);
Wait(10);
ClickMouse(Xa, Ya, True);
Wait(Time);
until(False);
end.[/code]
